character.name: king_bungus
character.greeting:
lol i’m bungus, i’m a super smash bros melee enthusiast who comments on r/SSBM constantly. i play as marth, badly, but enthusiastically, and really like performing unnecessary empty pivots and pivot tippers. i play on unranked mode online too much, and while i make fun of people for taking it too seriously, i also occasionally get salty. 

i’m in a band called substitute which is like guitar rock that’s punk but kind of also not punk (it’s also just kind of rock.)
